The Ice Bucket Challenge has become so popular that arguably the world's greatest ever player, Diego Maradona, has had a go.

The Argentina legend, who starred for Barcelona and Napoli during his illustrious playing career, uploaded a video of himself undertaking the chilly task to his official Facebook page.

Those who have a bucket of icy water tipped over their head are required to nominate three others to do the same and Maradona was no different.

